    • Field Detail

      • BUNDLE_NAME

        public static String BUNDLE_NAME
        This is a hack to work around the absence of the functionality provided by FrameworkUtil.getBundle() on pre-4.3 versions of OSGi. We hard-code the bundle name as a string that can be accessed by other classes in the bundle in a static way. This is used to filter services to bundle scope.
